OL,3,CJuly 4 General Election: How do you
OL,4,Cregister to vote and do you need ID?
OL,6,FRishi Sunak has called a General
OL,7,FElection for July 4, saying it was
OL,8,F"the moment for Britain to choose its
OL,9,Ffuture".
OL,11,FNow that the prime minister has set a
OL,12,Fdate, the countdown begins in what
OL,13,Fwill be the first UK General Election
OL,14,Fwhere all voters will have to show a
OL,15,Fvalid form of photo ID before casting
OL,16,Fa ballot.
OL,18,FHow do you register to vote, when is
OL,19,Fthe deadline and what sort of ID do
OL,20,Fyou need to have? ITV News explains.
