OL,3,CJuly 4 General Election: How do you
OL,4,Cregister to vote and do you need ID?
OL,6,FAnyone who wants to apply for a proxy
OL,7,Fvote ` in other words, for someone to
OL,8,Fvote on your behalf ` will have until
OL,9,FJune 26 to apply.
OL,11,FWhat happens next?
OL,13,FIf you intend on voting in person you
OL,14,Fwill receive a polling card in the
OL,15,Fpost that will tell you where to go.
OL,16,FYou will only be allowed to vote at
OL,17,Fthe address given on your card.
